msgid ":kbd:`o` key"
msgstr ":kbd:`o`"

#: ../../slideshow_tools/opengl_viewer.rst:66
msgid ""
"Move mouse in up-down-direction while pressing the right mouse button :kbd:"
"`c` key and use the scroll-wheel :kbd:`+` and :kbd:`-` keys :kbd:`ctrl` + "
"scrollwheel"
msgstr ""
"Pohybujte myšou nahor a nadol pri stlačenom pravom tlačidle myši, kláves :"
"kbd:`c` a použite rolovacie koliesko, klávesy :kbd:`+` a :kbd:`-`, :kbd:"
"`ctrl` + rolovacie koliesko"

